{"tid":2377740,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"resident evil RE : Verse trailer","createTime":"2021-01-24T01:06:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T20:44:10.000Z","uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3ead5e1c812995448de8de721f3f178a53b3a814","tid":2377740,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T01:06:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uGoZTX23JXQ&amp;t=36s&amp;ab_channel=capcomasia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuGoZTX23JXQ%26t%3D36s%26ab_channel%3Dcapcomasia&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2TagqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=350f5f9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uGoZTX23JXQ&amp;t=36s&amp;ab_channel=capcomasia</a>"},{"pid":"cd2cb5f503d77dc2589a7c4dfde3a40fd1aeda8b","tid":2377740,"uid":34410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T01:07:44.000Z","msg":"SPEC<br />\n遊戲名稱：Resident Evil Re:Verse<br />\n<br />\n發佈日：預定為2021年<br />\n<br />\n平台：PlayStation&reg;4 / Xbox One / Steam<br />\n<br />\n※PlayStation&reg;5可遊玩PlayStation&reg;4版本；Xbox Series X可遊玩Xbox One版本。<br />\n<br />\n類型：多人動作<br />\n<br />\n遊玩人數：4～6人<br />\n<br />\n評級：18+<br />\n※《RE:VERSE》為收錄於《Resident Evil Village》內的線上專用遊戲。<br />\n另外，遊玩本作時需要連接網絡。<br />\n<br />\nABOUT<br />\n為所有Resident Evil支持者獻上夢幻的競賽！<br />\n<br />\n《Resident Evil Re:Verse》是由四至六名玩家進行死亡競賽的「生存恐怖對戰遊戲」。<br />\n大家熟悉的Resident Evil系列角色，以及充滿威脅的B.O.W.將一同進行極限之戰。<br />\n規則採取「5分鐘一局的分數競賽方式」，無論途中被擊敗多少次，只要在最後得分最高便為之勝出。<br />\n利用設置於關卡內的武器和道具，盡可能打倒更多敵人吧！<br />\n<br />\n以「B.O.W.復仇」反攻！<br />\n<br />\n玩家角色一旦被擊倒，肉體便會變異為超強的B.O.W.(有機生命體兵器)，可以反攻其他玩家。<br />\n關卡內會出現「病毒」，持有越多，變身成的B.O.W.就會越強大。<br />\n活用B.O.W.的能力成功復仇，就是賺取大量分數的機會！<br />\n<br />\n感覺有d膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da094575cb5497f624bc2e49b51b47a8de966751","tid":2377740,"uid":48957,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"repl